8.11	Fauchon	Fauchon	Fauchon is a French gourmet food company that was founded in 1886 by Auguste Fauchon. The company is based in Paris, France and operates retail outlets. Fauchon currently produces tea, chocolate, biscuits and sweets among other products.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Paris_Fauchon_Christmas.jpg/220px-Paris_Fauchon_Christmas.jpg
